---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL.replace(/\/$/, '');
const featured = [
  { src: '/images/床上.jpg', cap: '床上耍廢' },
  { src: '/images/醜.jpg', cap: '耍醜時刻' },
  { src: '/images/趴地.jpg', cap: '趴地放空' },
  { src: '/images/玩具.jpg', cap: '玩具時間' },
];
---
<Base title="小乖果實" current="home">
  <section class="hero">
    <h1>哈囉，我是小乖 🐶</h1>
    <p>安安^^歡迎來到小乖世界！</p>
  </section>

  <article class="card">
    <p>我毛茸茸的，很可愛吧～但想摸我，必須交出食物來唷。</p>
    <p>而且食物當然有規定，我可不是隨便的小狗呢：</p>
    <ul class="foods">
      <li>最好的食物當然就是 <span class="highlight">牛肉</span> 啦！</li>
      <li>香噴噴的 <span class="highlight">香腸</span> 跟 <span class="highlight">鹹酥雞</span> 我也很愛吃 &gt;&lt;</li>
      <li>雞肉跟豬肉，還有各種零食我也吃</li>
    </ul>
    <p>雖然我很貪吃，但我個性溫順，從來不咬人，而且很聽話顧家哦！想看更多的我，自己去逛逛吧～</p>
  </article>

  <h2>大頭乖</h2>
  <div class="grid">
    {featured.map((p) => (
      <a class="photo" href={base + p.src} target="_blank" rel="noopener">
        <img src={base + p.src} alt={p.cap} loading="lazy" />
        <figcaption>{p.cap}</figcaption>
      </a>
    ))}
  </div>
</Base>
